1
00:00:07,260 --> 00:00:11,740
=Half-awake=

2
00:00:11,820 --> 00:00:15,420
=Episode 24=

3
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:22,480
Pack your things.

4
00:00:22,600 --> 00:00:23,440
We're leaving now.

5
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:43,880
You rushed back just for this photo?

6
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:49,680
Chu Muzhi was right.

7
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,680
You're really pitiful.

8
00:00:58,440 --> 00:00:59,280
No.

9
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,760
What Chu Muzhi said isn't true.

10
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,120
Don't believe him.

11
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:05,600
He... he... he...

12
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:06,920
He said that just to provoke me.

13
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:12,360
But it's fine.

14
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,280
I still have you.

15
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:17,560
You'll stay with me, right?

16
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:18,520
No way.

17
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,120
No.

18
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,320
No.

19
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:30,480
None of this is real.

20
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:33,290
You're lying to me, aren't you?

21
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,160
I am lying to you.

22
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,840
I've been lying to you all along,
Gu Yixiao.

23
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,720
I never loved you.

24
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,960
I could never love you.

25
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,400
Every day I spent with you,

26
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,600
it was all an act.

27
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:59,080
I forced myself to get close to you,

28
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:03,000
just to get the evidence against you,

29
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,000
so I could bring you down for good.

30
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:09,480
No.

31
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,200
That's not true.

32
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,800
You're lying to me, aren't you?

33
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:18,290
I've already handed the evidence
to the police.

34
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:20,760
They'll be here any minute.

35
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,600
No matter where you run,

36
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,640
it won't help.

37
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:29,600
Xingwan.

38
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:30,920
Xingwan.

39
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,520
You said it yourself.

40
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,560
You said you'd always be mine.

41
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,040
You even promised

42
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,160
to marry me.

43
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,320
You can't break your promise.

44
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,320
Gu Yixiao,

45
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,480
how desperate are you for love?

46
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,760
I don't like you.

47
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,160
I never like you at all.

48
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:52,440
Stop talking.

49
00:02:52,450 --> 00:02:53,450
I even dislike you.

50
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,800
- Stop it.
- I despise you.

51
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:56,080
Every single day with you,

52
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,600
I'm thinking how to make you disappear.

53
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,960
Stop talking!

54
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:14,080
I'm giving you two choices now.

55
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,360
Either come with me,

56
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,040
or stay with me till the end.

57
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,120
Which will it be?

58
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:31,880
I'm not choosing.

59
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,520
Gu Yixiao,

60
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,760
you should turn yourself in

61
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,960
and face the judgment of the law.

62
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:52,160
Think about what you did to me before.

63
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,680
How do you even have the nerve

64
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,040
to bargain with me now?

65
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:58,320
You

66
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:02,120
don't deserve to have love.

67
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:15,040
I truly wanted to love everyone.

68
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:17,880
My family.

69
00:04:18,280 --> 00:04:19,800
My brothers, my love.

70
00:04:27,900 --> 00:04:28,900
You must be dying to know

71
00:04:28,900 --> 00:04:30,300
the answer to that question, right?

72
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,520
Why did your mom leave you back then?

73
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,240
Because

74
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,400
she simply didn't love you.

75
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,400
I have one last question for you.

76
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,360
Back then,

77
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:48,560
who was really trying to hurt Gu Yixiao?

78
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,000
It was me.

79
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:59,080
He should never have been born.

80
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:04,240
His very existence was a mistake.

81
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:13,840
Did you hear that?

82
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,160
No one needs you.

83
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,960
You gave it everything you had,

84
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:32,120
and still ended up with nothing.

85
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,600
Your whole life,

86
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,880
from start to finish,

87
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,640
has been a complete joke.

88
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:48,760
You say things like that

89
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:52,160
because you want to avenge your family?

90
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,960
No, Gu Yixiao.

91
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,360
I only just realized now

92
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,760
that revenge

93
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:06,440
isn't the only way to fix things.

94
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:08,520
But you

95
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:13,200
still have to pay

96
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,000
for the wrongs you've done.

97
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:20,680
Go ahead.

98
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:22,040
Turn yourself in.

99
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,720
Confess to what you've done.

100
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,200
Just leave.

101
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,360
Here come the Longevity Noodles.

102
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,200
Xiao, it's your birthday.

103
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:48,550
You have to eat Longevity Noodles.

104
00:06:48,550 --> 00:06:50,330
That's how you'll grow up
healthy and strong,

105
00:06:50,330 --> 00:06:51,380
and live a long, long life.

106
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:52,440
A long, long life.

107
00:06:52,450 --> 00:06:56,090
♪If not once devoured by blazing flames♪

108
00:06:56,090 --> 00:06:59,250
♪Who would ever understand
this baptism by fire♪

109
00:06:59,250 --> 00:07:02,330
♪You betrayed me so decisively♪

110
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:06,030
♪With indifference laid bare♪

111
00:07:06,110 --> 00:07:09,210
♪It taught me to stay silent first♪

112
00:07:09,210 --> 00:07:12,700
♪So the explosion would be deafening♪

113
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:13,720
Dad.

114
00:07:14,030 --> 00:07:20,270
♪A burning soul tears off
its own shackles♪

115
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:26,460
♪The stubborn pain
hardens into the hottest flame♪

116
00:07:26,470 --> 00:07:27,840
From the day I met you,

117
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:30,040
my life completely fell apart.

118
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:31,840
It was you.

119
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:32,880
Your appearance

120
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,110
turned me into who I am now.

121
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,020
I don't want to fight you.

122
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,880
But Ye Xingwan is my bottom line.

123
00:07:41,690 --> 00:07:44,550
♪Your screams sound like regret to me♪

124
00:07:44,550 --> 00:07:48,920
♪Greed caused the chaos,
none can run away♪

125
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,720
You believe me now, right?

126
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:53,680
I do.

127
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:57,680
But it's already too late.

128
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,960
How could you be this naive?

129
00:08:11,220 --> 00:08:13,700
(Two unread messages)

130
00:08:13,700 --> 00:08:15,400
(Gu Yixiao)

131
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,240
(Xingwan,)

132
00:08:17,100 --> 00:08:18,520
(I want to love you wholeheartedly.)

133
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:20,960
(I think,)

134
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,080
(from the very beginning,)

135
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,960
(I've always loved you.)

136
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,400
(If)

137
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,960
(we could start over,)

138
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:32,720
(I wish)

139
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,440
(you hadn't saved me back then.)

140
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:41,230
♪A burning soul tears off
its own shackles♪

141
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,960
♪The stubborn pain♪

142
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:50,960
♪Hardens into the hottest flame♪

143
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:55,720
♪Taste the fruit you planted,
don't ask me for mercy♪

144
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:59,290
♪Just enjoy this searing pain♪

145
00:08:59,290 --> 00:09:02,460
♪See whether blood or tears flow first♪

146
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:05,520
♪Your screams sound like regret to me♪

147
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:09,860
♪Greed caused the chaos,
none can run away♪

148
00:09:09,860 --> 00:09:13,420
♪The karma you sowed by your own hands♪

149
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:16,520
♪Watered to maturity
with blood and tears♪

150
00:09:16,730 --> 00:09:19,300
♪I pick it myself, for you to taste♪

151
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:23,200
♪Face the bitter fruit you made♪

152
00:09:37,010 --> 00:09:41,580
