161
00:10:15,340 --> 00:10:16,180
(Thanks to timely rescue, Gu Yixiao
survived and turned himself in.)

162
00:10:16,180 --> 00:10:17,020
(He received a fair trial
according to law.)

163
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:17,860
(The police launched
a full-scale operation.)

164
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:18,700
(They completely dismantled
the criminal gang.)

165
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:19,540
(All core members were arrested.)

166
00:10:19,540 --> 00:10:20,380
(Ye Xingwan received lenient treatment
for turning herself in.)

167
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:21,220
(All remaining illegal activities
of the group were fully uncovered.)

168
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,080
(What awaits them now
is the full weight of the law.)

169
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,520
Back on campus again,

170
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:35,620
are you getting used to it?

171
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,400
What brings you here?

172
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:41,920
This photo was sent to me by Xingyue.

173
00:10:42,300 --> 00:10:43,500
She asked me to give it to you.

174
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:51,720
This one

175
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,600
was taken on my birthday last year.

176
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,560
Make a wish.

177
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:12,440
What did you wish for?

178
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,040
The first wish.

179
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,920
Gu Yixiao gives me a white dress.

180
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,200
The second wish.

181
00:11:22,900 --> 00:11:24,540
Gu Yixiao takes me
to the amusement park.

182
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:26,760
The third wish.

183
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:31,000
Gu Yixiao says he loves me.

184
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,120
But he doesn't know

185
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,240
I was lying to him.

186
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,490
There's something I've always
wanted to ask you.

187
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,880
When Gu Yixiao pointed a gun
at you back then,

188
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,440
why didn't you run?

189
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:47,480
What if he lost control
and ended up killing you?

190
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,080
He would never kill me.

191
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,600
Because his right hand

192
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:55,850
couldn't pull the trigger.

193
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,200
Anyway, it's all behind us now.

194
00:12:02,300 --> 00:12:03,700
The future will get better for sure.

195
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:05,800
The good thing is,

196
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:10,000
I never gave up hope.

197
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:11,880
Go to class.

198
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,920
Alright.

199
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:26,800
Xingwan.

200
00:12:43,040 --> 00:12:44,400
(If hatred is a cage,)

201
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,280
