202
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,560
(only forges stronger chains.)

203
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:51,600
(Only letting go)

204
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,080
(is the key to unlocking the cage)

205
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:57,560
(to free the self
that's been imprisoned.)

